sentences.english: The agreement needed to be in place prior to commencing the work.
sentences.chinese: 协议需要在工作开始之前就到位。

sentences.english: Even the dye will have more depth and richness.
sentences.chinese: 其色调也染得更加到位和饱满。

sentences.english: Conclusion Take some effective measures to enhance the transferring rate of TB patients successfully.
sentences.chinese: 结论采取有效的措施，提高病人的转诊到位率。

sentences.english: Customarily, the austerity measures have to be in place as the aid package takes effect.
sentences.chinese: 在援助计划生效的同时，紧缩措施通常必须到位。

sentences.english: The new box could be epoxied or screw attached into place.
sentences.chinese: 该新盒可以用用环氧树脂粘合或螺栓连接到位。

sentences.english: Salaries have been distributed to every worker up to yesterday.
sentences.chinese: 截止到昨天，工资已经全部发付到位。

sentences.english: The site "three connections and one leveling" condition is available.
sentences.chinese: 现场三通一平工作已到位。

sentences.english: When the blank is on the set,the feeding signal will be switched out automatically.
sentences.chinese: 坯料到位后，送给信号则自动从电路中断开。

sentences.english: The Tessellation optimization is not truly in place.
sentences.chinese: 在没有真正到位镶嵌优化。

sentences.english: I think Jones captured jungle warfare brilliantly.
sentences.chinese: 我认为琼斯把握丛林战非常到位。

sentences.english: Fourth, in place for customer service…
All the preparation work is done.
sentences.chinese: 目前，准备工作已经到位。

sentences.english: It means preventive controls were either not in place or not used effectively.
sentences.chinese: 它表明预防控制措施没有到位，或者没有发挥好作用。

sentences.english: His depiction of finance's failures is not novel- however it is well done.
sentences.chinese: 他对金融业失败的描述并不希奇，却相当到位。

sentences.english: To lessen the resonance from the HDD I used rubber rings to mount it in place.
sentences.chinese: 为了减少从硬盘我用橡胶圈装入到位的共鸣。

sentences.english: The disbursement rate of local supporting fund is comparatively low.
sentences.chinese: 地方配套资金到位率较低。
